Class Controller

java.lang.Object
fr.formiko.kokcinelo.Controller
public class Controller extends Object

      public void moveAphids()
      Move aphids. Aphids first run away from the closest ladybug they can see if they can see one. Else they move slowly to a random direction & some time change it. If they hit a wall, they change there wanted rotation angle for the nexts turns.
